<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Investment Rejected</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 20px; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: auto; border: 1px solid #eee; padding: 30px; border-radius: 10px; }
    .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px; }
    .header h2 { margin: 0; color: #e74c3c; font-size: 24px; }
    .content { margin-bottom: 25px; }
    .status-badge { 
        display: inline-block; 
        padding: 5px 15px; 
        background-color: #fdeaea; 
        color: #e74c3c; 
        border-radius: 5px; 
        font-weight: bold; 
        font-size: 14px; 
        margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .reason-box { 
        background-color: #f9f9f9; 
        border-left: 4px solid #e74c3c; 
        padding: 15px; 
        margin: 20px 0; 
        font-style: italic;
    }
    .details { font-size: 14px; color: #555; }
    .footer { margin-top: 40px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #999; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 20px; }
    .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        background-color: #2c3e50;
        color: #ffffff;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h2>Investment Update</h2>
      <p>Reference #<%= investment.investmentRef %></p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p>Dear <%= user.firstName %>,</p>
      
      <p>We regret to inform you that your investment request for <strong><%= outlet.outletName %></strong> has been <strong>Rejected</strong> by the administration team.</p>
      
      <div class="status-badge">REJECTED</div>

      <div class="reason-box">
        <strong>Reason for Rejection:</strong><br>
        <%= reason %>
      </div>

      <div class="details">
        <p><strong>Investment Details:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Outlet: <%= outlet.outletName %></li>
          <li>Shares: <%= investment.shares %></li>
          <li>Total Amount: Rs. <%= investment.totalAmount %></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <p>If this was due to an incorrect payment screenshot or UTR number, you can initiate a new investment request from your dashboard.</p>
      
      <a href="<%= process.env.FRONTEND_URL %>/dashboard" class="button">Go to Dashboard</a>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>If you have any questions regarding this rejection, please contact our support team.</p>
      <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Your Company Name. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>